OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FA man who chased another man into
OL,8,Ftraffic with a machete in
OL,9,FSittingbourne has been jailed for 16
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FChris Maclean, admitted to the
OL,13,Fmanslaughter of Jay Gerrett, who died
OL,14,Fafter being hit by a car on St
OL,15,FMichael's Road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
