PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FThe incident happened just after 9pm
OL,8,Fon 2 August 2025. Maclean's co-
OL,9,Fdefendant, Jack Hunt, led Mr Gerrett
OL,10,Fto Pembury Street to sell him drugs. A
OL,11,Fconversation occurred between the two
OL,12,Fin the road, which police say quickly
OL,13,Fescalated into shouting.
OL,15,FHunt, 33, then called for support from
OL,16,FMaclean and another man, who exited
OL,17,Ftheir homes on Pembury Court and
OL,18,Fjoined the altercation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
