OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FKent Police say Maclean 'goaded' his
OL,8,Fvictim into fighting before
OL,9,Fbrandishing a large knife, swinging it
OL,10,Fwildly at his body and face.
OL,12,FWhile attempting to flee, Gerrett,
OL,13,Ffell down a grass verge into oncoming
OL,14,Ftraffic on St Michael's Road and was
OL,15,Ffatally hit by a car.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FMaclean was arrested in Canterbury on
OL,8,F5 August following CCTV and house-to-
OL,9,Fhouse enquiries, during which he
OL,10,Fpretended to have no knowledge of the
OL,11,Fincident. Upon his arrest, officers
OL,12,Funcovered a quantity of cocaine.
OL,14,FMaclean was charged with murder and
OL,15,Fpossession of a class A drug with
OL,16,Fintent to supply. He pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fthe possession of a class A drug with
OL,18,Fintent to supply at a Maidstone Crown
OL,19,FCourt hearing on 5 December.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FDenying he had murdered Mr Gerrett, a
OL,8,Fthree-week trial was set to begin on
OL,9,FTuesday 24 February 2026, but on the
OL,10,Ffirst day, Maclean offered a plea of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter which was accepted by
OL,12,Finvestigators and the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service. He also admitted
OL,14,Fto the drug-dealing offence.
OL,16,FThe 43-year-old was sentenced on
OL,17,FThursday 26 February to 16 years in
OL,18,Fprison. He was also deemed a dangerous
OL,19,Foffender.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FCo-defendant Hunt, of Platinum Way,
OL,8,FBorden, pleaded guilty to possessing
OL,9,Fcocaine with intent to supply and will
OL,10,Fbe sentenced at Maidstone Crown Court
OL,11,Fon Friday 1 May.
OL,13,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,14,FChief Inspector Zoe Traynor said:
OL,15,F"Maclean delayed accepting his
OL,16,Fresponsibility in causing the death of
OL,17,FJay Gerrett until the last minute,
OL,18,Fheaping anguish on his victim's family.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772182876
OL,3,CMan jailed for manslaughter after
OL,4,Cchasing another man into traffic with
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,F"We are very pleased that the
OL,8,Finvestigation we completed has led to
OL,9,Fjustice and the jailing of a violent
OL,10,Fman who had no hesitation in wielding
OL,11,Fa machete at a stranger in public.
OL,13,F"We hope today's sentence brings some
OL,14,Fclosure to Jay's family."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
